overview: ONE Championship: Mark Of Greatness was a Combat sport event held by ONE Championship on December 6, 2019 at the Axiata Arena in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia.  In the main event, legendary Muay Thai World Champion Sam-A Gaiyanghadao looks to capture his second ONE World Title, as he takes on Chinese kickboxing World Champion Wang Junguang for the inaugural ONE Strawweight Kickboxing World Championship.
title: ONE Championship 105: Mark Of Greatness
